AnalogChannel
           
Channel
          "Channels represent the various signal generation and measurement capabilities that are needed in a particular experiment(IQ, Analog or FastBias, for example), and are assigned names by the user." In the Device class, for example, a channel connects a physical device to an experimental parameter.
